reviewText: If you like men with extremely small genitals, like laughably small and not circumcised, this is your movie. I've never seen a film with so much flaccid genitals on display in passionate scenes. Some of these dudes should have been embarrassed to even show themselves on film because of their extreme lack of size.

This film is not Michelle Bauer at her most erotic as one reviewer (who rated it 5 stars!) claims. The film features more male nudity than I've ever seen in a softcore flick. Not worth the price or the time to watch naked dudes getting whipped and spanked. Legendary gay director David DeCoteau tricked a lot of viewers in to thinking this was a softcore "Basic Instinct" clone...it's is...but with lots of naked dudes. More male nudity than female.

Michelle Bauer and Deanne Power star as two gorgeous women who can't control their voracious sexual appetites for younger men. Follow their NAKED INSTINCT pushing passion to the limit. An extremely erotic film. The perfect 10, Michele Bauer, at her most erotic!
